title: The Secret Life of A Mochi
body:
by Feysand4Ever

Jimin to the outside world is just another dancer. But, secretly, at night, he goes to an apartment he rented out and holds gatherings for other “artists” who are everything from singers, rappers, and dancers to painters and fashion designers. They create backdrops and outfits for performances to songs and dances they create, but wear masks, so no one knows their real identities. (Alternate universe where the members of the music groups are not in the groups)
